'''Xero'''是一所主要研发[[雲端運算|云计算]][[會計系統|會計系統]]的软件公司，主要服务对象是中小型企业。Xero的总部位于新西兰[[惠灵顿|惠灵顿]]，并在澳大利亚、英国<ref name="PandoDailyBillion">{{Cite news|url=http://pando.com/2013/05/01/xero-a-billion-dollar-software-company-that-had-five-years-in-stealth-at-the-bottom-of-the-planet/|title=Xero: A billion-dollar software company that had five years in stealth at the bottom of the planet|last=McKenzie|first=Hamish|date=1 May 2013|publisher=|newspaper=Pando Daily|accessdate=15 January 2014|location=|pages=|language=|coauthors=|archive-date=2021-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314053648/https://pando.com/2013/05/01/xero-a-billion-dollar-software-company-that-had-five-years-in-stealth-at-the-bottom-of-the-planet/}}</ref>和美国设有分公司。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://smallbiztrends.com/2013/10/xero-small-business-accounting-software-funding.html|title=Small Biz Accounting Software Space Heats Up As Xero Raises $150 Million|last=Campbell|first=Anita|date=13 October 2013|publisher=Small Biz Trends|accessdate=15 January 2014|location=|pages=|language=|coauthors=|archive-date=2021-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418094459/https://smallbiztrends.com/2013/10/xero-small-business-accounting-software-funding.html}}</ref>[https://www.xero.com/nz/about/investors/listing/ Xero在澳大利亚证券交易所上市。] {{Wayback|url=https://www.xero.com/nz/about/investors/listing/ |date=20210925215312 }}<ref name="ZNSAAS"></ref>

Xero的产品以[[软件即服务|软件即服务]]（SaaS）为基础框架。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.smh.com.au/business/sharemarket-darling-xero-dubbed-apple-of-accounting-20131106-2x0m7.html|title=Sharemarket darling Xero dubbed ‘Apple of accounting’|last=Robins|first=Brian|date=6 November 2013|publisher=The Sydney Morning Herald|accessdate=15 January 2014|location=|pages=|language=|coauthors=|archive-date=2022-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220329214408/https://www.smh.com.au/business/sharemarket-darling-xero-dubbed-apple-of-accounting-20131106-2x0m7.html}}</ref>

== 发展历史 ==
Xero是由Rod Drury和一部分会计师创立的，Xero认为传统的[[应用软件|应用软件]]已经过时并决定建立一个现代化的云计算产品。<ref name="NZListenerHero"></ref>2006年，Xero 在新西兰[[惠灵顿|惠灵顿]]正式成立。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bizjournals.com/denver/news/2013/10/10/san-francisco-accounting-software.html|title=New Zealand accounting software company expanding to Denver|last=Calvey|first=Mark|date=10 October 2013|publisher=Denver Biz Journal|accessdate=15 January 2014|location=|pages=|language=|coauthors=|archive-date=2015-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150318001051/http://www.bizjournals.com/denver/news/2013/10/10/san-francisco-accounting-software.html}}</ref>2011年，Xero进军[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]市场，<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.smartcompany.com.au/growth/economy/27628-myob-vs-xero-the-accountancy-software-joust.html|title=MYOB vs Xero: The accountancy software joust|last=Wallace|first=Aaron|date=29 August 2012|publisher=Smart Company|accessdate=15 January 2014|location=|pages=|language=|coauthors=|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924103054/http://www.smartcompany.com.au/growth/economy/27628-myob-vs-xero-the-accountancy-software-joust.html}}</ref>2012年，Xero进军英国市场<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/business/marketforceslive/2013/sep/25/sage-competition-concerns-xero|title=Sage slips  on competition  concerns as rival Xero targets UK|last=Fletcher|first=Nick|date=25 September 2013|publisher=The Guardian|accessdate=15 January 2014|location=|pages=|language=|coauthors=|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411040842/http://www.theguardian.com/business/marketforceslive/2013/sep/25/sage-competition-concerns-xero}}</ref>和美国市场。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://news.dice.com/2013/10/17/accounting-software-maker-xero-hiring-in-sf-143/|title=Accounting Software Maker Xero Hiring in S.F.|last=Thomas|first=Myra|date=17 October 2013|publisher=Dice|accessdate=15 January 2014|location=|pages=|language=|coauthors=|archive-date=2014-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140220225610/http://news.dice.com/2013/10/17/accounting-software-maker-xero-hiring-in-sf-143/}}</ref>

=== 资金状况 ===
2007年6月5日，Xero在[[新西兰证券交易所|新西兰证券交易所]]1500万美元（[[紐西蘭元|NZD]]）[[首次公开募股|首次公开募股]]并在其首个交易日获得15％的股份。<ref name="NZStock">{{Cite news|url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/business/news/article.cfm?c_id=3&objectid=10443821|title=Xero begins strongly|last=Niesche|first=Christopher|date=6 June 2007|publisher=|newspaper=New Zealand Herald|accessdate=15 January 2014|location=|pages=|language=|coauthors=|archive-date=2018-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180713043210/https://www.nzherald.co.nz/business/news/article.cfm?c_id=3&objectid=10443821}}</ref>为了防止上市后Xero会迫于压力被出售给竞争对手，Xero不在美国[[硅谷|硅谷]]上市。<ref name="PandoDailyBillion">{{Cite news|url=http://pando.com/2013/05/01/xero-a-billion-dollar-software-company-that-had-five-years-in-stealth-at-the-bottom-of-the-planet/|title=Xero: A billion-dollar software company that had five years in stealth at the bottom of the planet|last=McKenzie|first=Hamish|date=1 May 2013|publisher=|newspaper=Pando Daily|accessdate=15 January 2014|location=|pages=|language=|coauthors=}}</ref>2012年11月8日，Xero在[[澳洲證券交易所|澳洲證券交易所]]上市。<ref name="ZNSAAS"></ref>

=== 收购记录 ===
自成立以来，Xero收购了许多公司。2011年7月，Xero收购了[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]公司Paycycle。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/business/5323260/Xero-buys-payroll-provider-to-boost-Australian-growth|title=Xero buys payroll firm to boost Aust growth|accessdate=19 September 2013|last=Rogers|first=Claire|publisher=Stuff.co.nz|archive-date=2016-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160813064106/http://www.stuff.co.nz/business/5323260/Xero-buys-payroll-provider-to-boost-Australian-growth}}</ref>2012年7月，Xero收购Spotlight Workpapers。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.idealog.co.nz/news/2012/07/xeros-latest-acquisition-compelling-one-accountants|title=Xero’s latest acquisition a ‘compelling’ one for accountants|accessdate=19 September 2013|publisher=Idealog|archive-date=2013-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023060047/http://www.idealog.co.nz/news/2012/07/xeros-latest-acquisition-compelling-one-accountants}}</ref>同年，Xero收购了WorkflowMax。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://diversity.net.nz/xero-raises-another-round-and-acquires-workflowmax/2012/02/01/|title=Xero Raises Another Round and Acquires WorkFlowMax|last=Kepes|first=Ben|date=1 February 2012|publisher=|newspaper=Diversity Limited|accessdate=17 January 2014|location=|pages=|language=|coauthors=|archive-date=2022-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220217104511/https://www.diversity.net.nz/xero-raises-another-round-and-acquires-workflowmax/2012/02/01/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.startupsmart.com.au/buy-a-business/xero-acquires-max-solutions-after-raising-$15m/201202025260.html|title=Xero acquires Max Solutions after raising $15m|accessdate=19 September 2013|last=Hammond|first=Michelle|publisher=Startup Smart|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924105810/http://www.startupsmart.com.au/buy-a-business/xero-acquires-max-solutions-after-raising-$15m/201202025260.html}}</ref>2013年，Xero进军美国市场。<ref name="xero fades">{{Cite news|url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/business/industries/10297744/US-interest-in-Xero-fades|title=US interest in Xero fades|date=23 July 2014|work=Businessday|publisher=Fairfax Media|accessdate=2016-04-02|archive-date=2017-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170924081052/http://www.stuff.co.nz/business/industries/10297744/US-interest-in-Xero-fades}}</ref>

