2014年2月24日，[[微软|微软]]和[[通用汽车|通用汽车]]纽约总部的前任首席财务官Chris Liddell成为了董事会的新任主席。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://blogs.wsj.com/digits/2014/02/11/xero-steps-up-u-s-attack-with-chris-liddell-as-chairman/|title=Xero Steps Up U.S. Attack With Chris Liddell as Chairman|accessdate=2015-12-31|date=2014-02-11|last=Clark|first=Don|website=WSJ Blogs - Digits|archive-date=2019-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402122141/https://blogs.wsj.com/digits/2014/02/11/xero-steps-up-u-s-attack-with-chris-liddell-as-chairman/}}</ref>

